{
  "texts": [
    "However, this concern has not yet been translated into discourse around the ethical implementation of generative AI for business.",
    "This is evidenced by the lack of awareness or concern around the cyber security risk of gen AI amongst business leaders [11].",
    "This paper therefore makes the following contributions:• Supports the case for cyber security being an ethical obligation for business, using normative ethical principles.",
    "• Highlights literature on the cyber security risks associated with generative AI, including the risks of poisoning, manipulation, and data leakage.",
    "• Demonstrates how the risks associated with generative AI can threaten business operations and their responsibilities to stakeholders."
  ]
}